rComments: Amazing teacher, comfortable and relaxed class environment. Great at explaining things to beginner students of German. One of the best at U of T!

Prof Noyes is great at teaching the German Lit course - he engages the class lots but not to the point of it being annoying. His discussions are interesting and helpful and he makes the material accessible without dumbing it down.
Extremely enjoyable course. I enjoyed the careful & close readings & the attention to students' participation.
Excellent provacative class. Noyes is a great professor.
